        <a target="_blank" href="https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-js2/Syncfusion.EJ2.Charts.ChartEmptyPointSettings.html#Syncfusion_EJ2_Charts_ChartEmptyPointSettings_Mode" aria-label="Navigate to the Mode property reference for ChartEmptyPointSettings">Mode</a> is <b>Gap</b>.
